sonarr_episodefile_episodeoverviews: After killing Phibrizzo, a barrier that was holding them in for a thousand of years (or so), has been removed, arranged by Phil (Amelia's father.)  Lina gets a letter from someone named Filia, who wants to meet her and offers her money (something Lina can't refuse.)
